Summary A reliable self-starter with a passion for technology and a proven Product & Project Management track record within online and mobile software services that have particularly focused on content management and content delivery. I am able to grasp novel concepts quickly and easily adapt to new working environments – whether engaged within a sole operational role or as a personable, collaborative member or manager of a driven team.  

An advocate and ardent practitioner of the three key disciplines that define and deliver a first class user experience - to always be learning from user data, ensuring constant attention to detail and never forgetting the importance of communicating with the relevant stakeholders. 

My experience has ranged from building start-up products through to managing complex software projects that required daily liaison with a broad range of contributory personnel from third parties - ranging from mobile network operators, companies such as Novell and RIM, regulatory Government departments or clients with multiple overseas offices. 

- Proven track record of successfully managing a broad range of software project life-cycles; 
- Android, iOS and Blackberry app experience; 
- Experienced in Agile and Scrum product management; 
- Experienced in using heat map, A/B testing and analytics software; 
- UX prototype and wire-framing ability; 
- Product based offline and digital marketing experience; 
- Hardware life cycle management experience; 
- Commercially adept and able to create, as well as manage, in-depth budget and P&L models; 
- Extensive supplier sourcing and partner relationship management experience; 
- Skilled and experienced at writing collateral, white papers and product documentation; 
